# Important Files for MCP Exercise Database Server

This project is an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for an exercise database written in TypeScript.

## Core Files

- `README.md` - Comprehensive project documentation (744 lines)
- `package.json` - Project configuration and dependencies
- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript configuration
- `railway.toml` - Railway deployment configuration (TOML format)
- `railway.json` - Railway deployment configuration (JSON format)
- `src/main.ts` - Main entry point for the MCP server (Express + SSE transport)
- `src/types.ts` - Shared TypeScript interfaces and types
- `data/exercises.json` - Exercise database (1300+ exercises)
- `.env` - Environment variables (not tracked in git)
- `.env.example` - Example environment configuration
- `.gitignore` - Git ignore patterns

## Exercise Functions

- `src/exercise-functions/loader.ts` - Data loading and exercise retrieval
- `src/exercise-functions/search.ts` - Search and filtering functions
- `src/exercise-functions/validation.ts` - Exercise ID validation
- `src/exercise-functions/alternatives.ts` - Finding alternative exercises
- `src/exercise-functions/metadata.ts` - Categories, equipment, muscle groups
- `src/exercise-functions/health.ts` - Database health monitoring and statistics
- `src/exercise-functions/performance.ts` - Performance metrics and integrity validation

## MCP Tools

- `src/tools/search-tools.ts` - Search-related MCP tools
- `src/tools/lookup-tools.ts` - Get by ID and validation tools
- `src/tools/filter-tools.ts` - Category and equipment filtering tools
- `src/tools/metadata-tools.ts` - Resource listing tools
- `src/tools/health-tools.ts` - Health monitoring and system information tools

## Development Files

- `dist/` - Compiled TypeScript output (ignored by git)
- `node_modules/` - Package dependencies (ignored by git)

